beer.beer_description:
Drawing influence from our brewer's San Diego heritage, Coast Ale is our take on the California common ale and
reminiscent of epic south coast
adventures, surfing & exploring with good friends. It’s fresh, crisp & clean with a rich malt body, fruity hop bitterness
and smooth rounded finish.
Best enjoyed up & down the coast.

ABV: 4.3% // Hops: Hallertau, Saaz, Dr Rudi
